author: Cleo Abram
description:
Sharks have a special sixth sense that makes them super effective apex predators. 

It helps them find prey deep under the sand and in dark, murky waters, navigate the oceans, and maybe even detect temperature changes. 

Can you guess what it is?   

If you believe there should be more optimistic science and tech stories, subscribe!

#shorts #sharks #ocean #science #animation
title: Sharks Have A Sixth Sense
